Nasrul-Lahi-Faith Society (NASFAT) Kaduna State branch has commissioned a  N15m Media and Administrative Centre in the state. The society said it required adequate media coverage for all its activities. The branch chairman, Engineer  Muhyideen Alimi Yusuf,  said the centre would serve as hub for Islamic propagation. He  commended the Ummah who partook in the building of the facility and  prayed for Allah to  reward them with Aljanah.